\id HAG Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93
\h AKAI
\toc1 AKAI
\toc2 Akai
\toc3 Ak
\mt1 AKAI
\ip Kamongome poropeta akali Akai lenge keta banya wambu pii lamaiyamo dupwa dakena pyasi palamo. Ee kana 520 W.K. dokopa Akaimi pii dusipa yapo nyepala pyao reteya. Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu wakale dupwana lanyuo peyaminyi doko range kamba epapala ee kana lapo yuu Jerusaleme dokona palyuo kareyaminyipape tembole anda angi doko mee lalyisi siya. Waili pii dapwa Isaraele wambunya lita dusipame tembole anda doko kamba pinya lao poraiyuo lamaiya. Anatu baame wambu dupwa mona kapu kyepala yapasi ingyuo kararaminyi dupwa kando au pyuo koo soo karena laro lao lalu lao leya. Anatunya tembole anda doko kwao sipyamopa mee wambu malu mee rangena anda keyange dokona palyuo pyuo pyuo karaminyi, Akaimi leya.
\c 1
\p 
